SUMMARY:Texas Sound Meditation with Leala\, Melissa\, and James
DESCRIPTION:Levy Park brings “Self Care” to a whole new level with Sound Healing led by Leala\, Melissa\, and James. \nA sound bath is a gentle\, nurturing\, and cathartic meditation experience for anyone looking to improve the quality of their life. This act of self-care is beneficial for anyone from beginners to advanced meditators who are ready to experience a greater sense of peace and well-being. \nThe Levy Park Sound Baths will assist in clearing out that which is blocking the natural vitality while strengthening the connection and balance between mind\, body\, and soul. A collectively cultivated safe space offers participants an opportunity to deepen their own journey of self-love\, healing or transformation. \nWhile relieving stress\, tension and anxiety this sound immersion experience will have you feeling revitalized\, relaxed and rejuvenate. Let the sounds wash away everything that no longer serves you as you set your intentions and manifest your desires! \n 
URL:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/events/sound-therapy-texas-sound/2026-06-16/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.levyparkhouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/New-Leala.jpg
END:VEVENT
